  "body": "### Description\r\nTeku runs `PeerChainValidator` for each status update from peers.  We should avoid requesting extra data from the peer for these updates if possible.  Most likely can just skip revalidating the peer's finalized chain after the initial validation is done. Should review for any other checks that are only required for the first status update.",
